data.description:
Sellers entertaining short sale offers, come take a look and make an offer, decision based on third party approval.

Investors, Flippers, Handy People this is for you! Take this once gem and turn it into your diamond. This multi family home has a one bedroom apartment ready for you live in or rent, while you redesign the lower portion of the home into what you want it to be. The unfinished portion of the home can offer up to three bedrooms, one plus baths, open kitchen living room area and a master bedroom with bath, if you choose. Looking for an investment property, turn this home in a fully finished multi unit and get your mortgage paid for. You also have the option of turning this into a single family home, come take a look and put your mind to work. The large two car garage is a great bonus to this home. Have a new home for the holidays and start 2024 off with a plan. Additional photos to come.
